com.st.olm.cq.api.ccc

Interface CCCAsset<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the wrapped type for the asset
    All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.sling.api.adapter.Adaptable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CCCFragmentAsset, CCCResourceAsset

    public interface CCCAsset<T>
extends org.apache.sling.api.adapter.Adaptable
    Represenents a CCCAsset. Essentially, CCCAssets can be either Fragments or Resources. Fragments will be backed by a Page whereas the Resources are backed by a File.
    Author:
    dklco
